    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "BONANZA\nAIR LINES\nFLYING\nTHE\nROUTE OF THE\nGOLD STRIKES\nRENO\nHAWTHORNE\nLAS VEGAS",
      "BONANZA AIR\nINC.\nSOUTHBOUND\nLINES\nNORTHBOUND\nLeave LAS VEGAS\nLeave TONOPAH\nLeave HAWTHORNE\nArrive RENO\nFARES\nLAS VEGAS to RENO\n9:00 A.M.\n10:00 A.M.\n10:40 A.M.\n11:30 A.M.\nLeave RENO\nLeave HAWTHORNE\nLeave TONOPAH\nArrive LAS VEGAS\nALL PACIFIC STANDARD TIME\n4:00 P.M.\n4:30 P.M.\n5:10 P.M.\n6:30 P.M.\n22.50\nLAS VEGAS to TONOPAH\n10.87\nFOR RESERVATIONS\nFor reservations Telephone Las Vegas 3100, Reno 2-6975\n(Durkee Travel Bureau), Tonopah 542 (Mizpah Hotel), and\nHawthorne 11 (Golden Key Drug).\nTIME LIMIT ON TICKETS\nLAS VEGAS to HAWTHORNE 16.63\nRENO to TONOPAH\n11.63\nRENO to HAWTHORNE\n5.88\nTONOPAH to HAWTHORNE\n5.75\nPlus Federal Transportation Tax\n10 PER CENT DISCOUNT ON\nALL ROUND TRIPS\nSCHEDULE SUBJECT TO CHANGE\nWITHOUT NOTICE\nTickets are valid for a period of four (4)\nmonths after date of issuance.\nRENO\nHAWTHORNE\nTONOPAH\nLAS VEGAS"
    ],
